Lieu CH, Chang YN, and Lai YK. Dual cytotoxic mechanisms of submicro-molar taxol on human leukemia HL-60 cells. Biochem Pharmacol. 53(11): 1587-1596, 1997
Lieu CW, Liu WT, Sun KH, and Wang SY. Some special characteristics of the novel human promonocyte cell line, HL-CZ. J Biomed Lab Sci 5: 196-204, 1993
Lieu CW, Lee SS, and Wang SY. The effect of Ganoderma lucidum on induction of differentiation in leukemic U937 cells. Anticancer Res. 12(4): 1211-1215, 1992
Wang SY, Wang RC, Chen LY, Lieu CW, Su SN, Yung CH, and Ho CK. Purification and characterization of human macrophage-derived granulomono-poietic enhancing factor (GM-EF). Exp Hematol 20: 552-557, 1992
